-- conclusion----
Predictive analysis transforms supply chain management from a static, reactive system to a dynamic, intelligent network.
By combining data modeling, real-time analytics, and AI forecasting, businesses can make proactive decisions that reduce costs, improve customer satisfaction, and maintain resilience even in uncertain conditions.


----Data Model----
Data Model (Small-Word Points)
Historical sales data
Order volume records
Customer demand patterns
Seasonal trend data
Regional sales data
Inventory levels
Supplier lead times
Production capacity
Logistics and delivery time
Pricing data
Promotion and discount data
Market trend indicators
External factors (weather, economy)
Product lifecycle data
Stock movement history
Returns and cancellations data
Real-time transaction data
Forecasted demand output
